### Alternative: Use actual endpoints directly via REST
### (for testing the raw API)

### Direct POST /v1/runners:run_prg with binary
POST http://192.168.0.120/v1/runners:run_prg
Content-Type: application/octet-stream

[binary PRG/SID data here]

