### Or with form data
POST http://192.168.0.120/v1/runners:sidplay
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=boundary

--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="sid"; filename="music.sid"
Content-Type: application/octet-stream

[binary SID data]
--boundary--
